Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.98,0:22:24.32,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}We are tossed by the waves of pain and tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.32,0:22:28.13,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}I'm tossed into the fray tossed by various fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:29.78,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}Wake up your brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.78,0:22:31.91,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}Flashed in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:34.42,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}It's a burst of sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:40.76,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}諦めがくれた安楽 沈滯の世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.76,0:22:46.72,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}いつからだっただろうふいに輝き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.72,0:22:50.01,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}変わらずにいてと願うこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:53.71,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}変わりゆく時に生きる僕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.71,0:22:56.77,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}本當の聲を言う得る夢を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:23:01.31,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}君と繋がった空へ響かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:05.21,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}もっと強くこの両手で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.21,0:23:08.49,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}涙全て振り払えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:11.77,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}今度こそは”呟く今と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.77,0:23:14.95,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}傷さえも無駄にしない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.95,0:23:18.35,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}もっと早く君のもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.35,0:23:21.64,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}たとえ羽根が千切れようとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.64,0:23:24.93,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}歪む世界 走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.93,0:23:28.21,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5}感覚のその向うへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.21,0:23:33.98,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur5\fad(0,800)}真実と加速してく
